# Snapshot: examples/06_let

### Source: `examples/06_let.frog`

```frog
proc main -- do
   1 2 3
   let a b c do
    a b c ? print print print
    c b a ? print print print
    a a a ? print print print
    b b b ? print print print
    c c c ? print print print
    c b c
   end
   ? print print print
end

```

### Run

Command:

```text
py -m frog run examples/06_let.frog
```

